title: Hour 3 - Russell Wilson Mile High Workout, John Smoltz
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Russell Wilson Mile High Workout, John Smoltz
description:
Dan talks about Denver Broncos QB Russell Wilson getting a workout in on the plane while his teammates were trying to sleep. And Hall of Fame Pitcher and MLB Analyst, john Smoltz drops by to preview the upcoming World Series between the Philadelphia Phillies and Houston Astros.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
